Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.82,0:00:35.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,将军事化的非人类组织起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:42.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,毁灭人类社会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:48.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不剩一人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.22,0:01:02.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1070.4,625)}仔细地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:01:02.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(774.4,626.6)}一丝不苟地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:01:02.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(496,626.6)}确认
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.26,0:01:02.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(235.2,629.8)}反复确认
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:04.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(940.8,588.2)}仔细寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:08.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}一个人都不剩地将地面上的人全部杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:13.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,毁灭人类让新生物接管世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.03,0:01:19.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,永远持续的美好的暗黑时代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:24.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,故此我的名字就叫做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.21,0:01:30.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「黑王」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:47.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔利那巷战之后几天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:57.36,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(445.333,197)\fad(350,500)}The Outlandish Knight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:57.36,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(180,106.334)\fad(350,500)}第十五幕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.66,0:01:53.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,交易成立
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.57,0:01:55.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就把粮食还有资金借给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:57.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,利息一点也不能少
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:01:59.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王要攻打过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:03.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前不得不让衰弱的奥尔特振兴起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:05.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了吗 圣日耳曼伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:08.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已经得到承诺了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:11.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还真能干呢 那个人妖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:12.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:14.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,公主大人太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:16.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 圣日耳曼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:19.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里偷窥的都是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.21,0:02:21.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:24.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,织田信长和那须与一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:26.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的还有汉尼拔巴卡老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:30.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还有总大将的岛津丰久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:32.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后还有你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:34.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔特真是狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:37.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流者一个接一个地漂流到那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:40.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你就没有感觉到有一股意志吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:41.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,来自某人的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:44.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:47.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们输了的话 所有都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:48.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,包括这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:50.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:52.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大方地援助我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:54.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,殷勤招待我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.79,0:02:57.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们吃好的用好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:03:02.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,帮助我们尽快振兴这个疲惫的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:04.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是说了些有趣的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:08.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我觉得只是给予你们援助就太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:11.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来做生意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:14.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔特有精灵对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:17.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个很美丽的人种
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:19.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 的确是有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但你在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.04,0:03:25.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,很多古彬连的有钱人都喜欢精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:27.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:29.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你想说让我们贩卖精灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:33.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,让精灵女性穿着可爱的制服在剧院里面唱歌跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:38.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为之倾心的年轻人就会大把大把地购买周边商品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:41.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,和精灵的握手会之类的应该能狠狠地赚一笔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:42.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这个可以有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:44.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事情当然是不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:46.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,让精灵进行接待的酒吧么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:48.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这个可以有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:48.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:52.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,让精灵的男性来接待富婆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也可以有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:55.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:04:01.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到安土城男公关部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:04.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是这里的负责人织田信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:08.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？费用太高了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:11.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就稍微来一下里面的事务所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:14.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦不妙啊 好适合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:16.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有点像真岛的哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:17.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:20.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你的指名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:22.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在下的源氏名是与一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:24.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,源氏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:27.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我取得店内营业额排名第一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:30.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 喝吧喝吧喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:32.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大把大把地挥霍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:35.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大把大把地挥霍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:38.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,热情已经在想像中高涨了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:45.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也总有一天会在威尔利那二丁目开店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:48.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集着熟客的我的小店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:49.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点啊 人妖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:51.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快回到现实中来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们错了 人妖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:28.31,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(69.334,261)}奥尔特北部 山脉森林地带
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:32.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们和奥尔特的战斗连战连胜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:35.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是因为天空神大人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:40.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后现在又有新的力量要加入我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:42.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是猫族一伙人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:47.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是为了和奥尔特战斗而集结起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:50.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我觉得你们犬人所说的天空神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:54.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,首先得好好证明他是否有资格当我们的头领
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:56.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你这只猫在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.05,0:06:58.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是对天空神大人的无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:02.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我一开始就不怎么愿意和你们这些狗辈一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:06.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你们还将举止如此随便的东西称为神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:09.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 起来啊神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:11.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们正在说你呢 神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:13.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,话说这个椅子是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:17.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,看呐 这个样子也算是神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.07,0:07:20.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在重要的结盟会议上睡迷糊了的神？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:22.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才说你们这些狗辈们真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:40.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:42.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,猫族第一的勇将阿梅杰居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:44.07,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,是魔术吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:44.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:48.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,猫啊 果然是猫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:54.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,猫族全部都跪拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:57.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是神 这是神的技艺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:08:00.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是猫呢 果然是猫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是动物王国么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:04.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,猫咪猫咪猫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:07.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,西庇阿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:10.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你说话应该是最快捷明了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:13.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是来自十月机关的联络 还很紧急
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:18.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王的军队终于要向南面前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:22.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕北方诸国会被陆续毁灭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:25.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦开始了就不会停止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:27.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,来到这里也只是时间的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:34.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在「北壁」所见的规模甚至算不上军队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:36.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 规模根本没得比
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:40.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候的兵力就已经把北壁打成那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:42.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可以立即告诉你答案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:43.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:47.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我们是不能和那种移动灾厄战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:50.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,南面的国家 奥尔特已经被漂流者所夺取
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:54.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现在那里正不断地集结着漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,战事一旦打响…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:57.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 玻利维亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:09:00.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,过得还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:04.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈 是的 玻利维亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:06.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我有信带给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:08.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,信么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:19.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,致于北方之地的日本飞行员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:23.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我从与我接触的自称十月机关的人口中听说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:26.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有人说着日语驾驶着飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:28.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这封信就是为了求证这个事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:34.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我是大日本帝国海军少将 山口多闻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:39.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在在南方的叫古彬连的商业岛国的岩礁之上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:47.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在和严重损害并触了礁的航空母舰「飞龙」一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:50.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有回信的意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:53.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就把这封信还给送信的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:09:59.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:06.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你还活着啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:12.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你这「行凶者多闻丸」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:16.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要来了 要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:18.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,终于要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:21.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们已经在北壁建立了根据地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:22.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是魔物的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:26.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,里面的状况正如弦上之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:28.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,弓已经拉满了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:32.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,北壁的门再次打开的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:33.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,会一口气涌过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:35.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就像山崩一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:38.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急往各个国家派遣使者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:41.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王废灭世界的长征要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:44.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,南伐 南伐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:46.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,长征之时已到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:49.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候要参与根绝人类的旅途了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:52.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,废弃世界之时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:53.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,废弃人类之时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:57.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王的大名将在天地间响彻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:01.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,打开大门
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:07.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,将人类世界变成非人世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:27.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,惟任光秀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:31.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,半人马的骑兵我就拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:34.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,让我放开手干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:37.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我信得过你的才干
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:39.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就像源平合战那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:44.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如同风火般迅速扰乱敌方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:48.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,先头部队的大将由土方阁下担当
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:51.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,应敌之策就由你定夺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:55.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不用理会后方的本阵 尽情上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:59.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是请绝对不要强攻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:01.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,土方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:04.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要出现伤兵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:06.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因为黑王大人会将他们全部都治好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:08.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一个不剩地全部治好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是多么弱的兵也好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.49,0:12:14.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是相应地也会让黑王大人使用力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:19.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以有兵负伤但存活下来的话 干脆让他死去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:24.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,阿纳斯塔西娅皇女殿下就在后方阵地待命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:27.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,会在合适的时机让你上场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:32.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,战争 不是太喜欢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:34.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因为好热
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:38.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不太懂自己的力量的使用方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:42.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,根据使用的方法甚至能够扭转战局
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:44.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斯普京殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:46.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,分化敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:47.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:50.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,即使没有内应但至少应该会互相猜疑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:57.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,最后都会把人类一个不剩地杀掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:13:00.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还有人会通敌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:02.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,当然会有 皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:05.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,人是种在被处刑之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:07.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,会想着只有自己能得救就好了的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:10.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后会为了延后自己被处刑的顺序
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:15.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而出卖别人来讨好处刑人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:19.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这种痛苦你不是也切身体会过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:22.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:27.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,惟任 我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:29.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,伤已经好了吗 贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:30.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:32.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,让我去把漂流者给烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:35.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,让我去把那个岛津丰久给烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:38.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那家伙 我要亲手把他烧死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:42.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要把他烧得灰都不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:44.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:49.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:51.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,请向我下令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.75,0:13:52.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,烧了他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:54.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,烧死他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:58.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,会烧 会让你烧的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:00.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以先待命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:08.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,惟任 发动战争
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:09.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,蹂躏他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:13.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,从北方的冻土到南方的北壁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:17.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,从西方的荒漠到东方的大海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:21.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,下至未出生的胎儿上到临终的老人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:23.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人都不留
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:25.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:26.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一丝不苟地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.18,0:14:28.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,确认
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:30.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,反复确认
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:36.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,无差别地 精心地将一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:41.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,将地面上的人一个不留地全部杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:47.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,开始进军
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:03.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等着 信长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:08.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你这蠢货 死了才好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:15.50,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(88,179.667)}「北壁」的南方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:15.50,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(138.667,277)}拉·兹纳酋长国境
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:15.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的 他们真的开始向南进军了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:18.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,正如十月机关那些家伙所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:20.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,发生大事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:22.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,立即召集各氏族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:24.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:27.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 但是啊 酋长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:32.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要 要和那种东西战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:39.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道北方部族的国家能够拖延多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:44.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在北壁沦陷之后也一直在戒备着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,拖延不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:50.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会像浸湿的纸被刺穿一样全数被灭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:53.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,结果正如那个叫信长的人所说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:57.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没有任何一个人把自己的军队交给漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:16:00.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,无论我们怎么向他们诉说黑王军的威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,蹂躏他们 蹂躏他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:05.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,进行革新
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:07.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,重建世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,弓箭没用 会被弹开的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:30.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还有狗头人骑在背上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:33.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么巨人族会穿着铠甲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:36.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么巨人族会和狗头人互相协助啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:54.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,全身覆盖青铜铠的巨人在立于部队前方蹂躏敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:58.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,骑在背上的狗头人和哥布林则警戒着周围
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,指挥巨人 支援巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:05.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,由巨人进行运送并压制敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.51,0:17:06.40,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,注：танковый десант(tankovyy desant)，即战车跨乘或称为步坦协同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.51,0:17:06.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「步坦协同」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:10.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道居然有这种战斗方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:18.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是飞龙从空中的支援
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:21.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还是空降士兵的战斗方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:26.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王为什么会知道这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:31.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他真的是我所想的「那个」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:34.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:37.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,无论他是谁还是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:40.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,能够杀死信长的话也就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:04.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,随便杀杀就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:06.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把恐怖埋入他们的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:09.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为了逃避灾难而向邻国逃跑的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:11.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,难民就会占满邻国城市的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:17.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来就不能随心所欲地召集和调动军队了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:20.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,难民也要吃饭拉屎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:24.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请变得越来越难受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:27.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,变得越来越容易沦陷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:35.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把你们所有人都烧起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:37.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是漂流者所占据的奥尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会给他们的巷道带来火焰与灰烬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:47.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德这家伙真是让人头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:49.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,乱烧一通
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:52.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,人类可是重要的资源啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:55.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要随便对待人类的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:57.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要非常珍重地对待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:01.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要稍微减轻一下黑王大人的负担
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:05.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,头发可以用来做火绒和绳子还有细绳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:06.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,肉是食物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:08.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,血是饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:11.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,皮用来做衣服和皮制品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:12.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,骨头用来做装饰品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:15.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「人类浑身上下都是宝」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:29.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:31.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我的心沸腾不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:34.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是在这种不知道哪里的巷道也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:37.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这应该是我所期待的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:39.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该是个渴战鬼才对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:42.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是最喜欢战争了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:43.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:50.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我的确非常享受和那个混账白痴的对殴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:54.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:56.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.28,0:19:57.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:59.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个堡垒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:00.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,尖塔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:03.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就像割草一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:05.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就像拍打白蚁一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:08.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就像去除小石头一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:11.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,向着下一个地方前进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:17.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,赢不了 我们的军队赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,集结残余兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,向南 向奥尔特前进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:27.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界的军队绝对赢不了那些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:29.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:32.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,能打倒不属于这个世界的生物的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:35.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,也就只有不属于这个世界的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:52.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把缰绳给我 混账
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,都跟你说过不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:20:56.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,让我操纵它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:20:59.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在天上飞…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:01.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已经到了 西庇阿大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:05.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.44,0:21:08.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:11.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是「多闻丸」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.05,0:21:17.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第三四三海军航空队 战斗第三〇一飞行队新选组队长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:19.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,菅野直大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:21.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我僭越 山口少将
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:23.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,请先和我相扑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:30.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你本应该在中途岛就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.30,0:21:32.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你说不定是个亡灵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:34.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以让我来把你摔一次试试
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:35.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 菅野大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:37.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我不认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:41.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大尉 你是什么时候被送到这里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:44.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,1945年8月1日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.34,0:21:47.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,天空神大人在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:50.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:54.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是蛮族之间的风俗习惯之类的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:56.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,日本怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:22:00.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,反正下场肯定很糟糕吧 大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:06.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然不问输赢之类的 不愧是你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.11,0:22:09.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在本来就没有胜算的那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:14.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟王牌的航空战队在我的眼前消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:25.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,全都如同灰烬一般了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.42,0:22:29.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,联合舰队都被摧毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:32.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:36.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是大和还是武藏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.30,0:22:39.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,都已经成为海中的碎屑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.44,0:22:43.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我来这边的时间并不长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.47,0:22:46.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,联合舰队还没有被毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.19,0:22:48.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,飞龙还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:53.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这里还有提督以及飞行员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:22:55.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只有两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.03,0:22:57.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们就是二航战
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.99,0:23:02.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,九九式舰载轰炸机
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.38,0:23:03.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,九七式舰上攻击机
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:05.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,零式舰载战斗机21型
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.49,0:23:07.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是破损的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:10.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没有一台正常的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.23,0:23:12.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不是没可能
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:15.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,炸弹和燃料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.65,0:23:17.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,几乎都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.28,0:23:20.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但还有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.61,0:23:25.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然分量不足以满足曾经的航空战队
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.85,0:23:27.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在这种场合
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:29.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 以这个世界的情况来说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:32.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只有能在天上飞的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.10,0:23:35.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,也会是足以逆转局势的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.76,0:23:39.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不过啊 这是真的飞龙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.78,0:23:41.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,其他船员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.86,0:23:42.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.28,0:23:46.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,来到这边的时候 舰上就只有我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.86,0:23:49.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,连尸体都没有一具
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.16,0:23:51.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.28,0:23:55.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那边那个像是在罗马歌剧里面出来的人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.68,0:23:58.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 可能意大利亚的艺人之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.88,0:23:59.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.76,0:24:01.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我是西庇阿·阿非利加努斯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.83,0:24:05.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的西庇阿是那个西庇阿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.59,0:24:06.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,布匿战争的那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.18,0:24:07.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.10,0:24:10.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,西庇阿 是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.67,0:24:13.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,话说我还是第一次听到你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.29,0:24:16.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,既然说是罗马就给我带个凯撒大帝来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.13,0:24:17.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过很多次了！很多次了！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.68,0:24:20.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个野蛮人真是讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.39,0:24:23.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,话说这个钢铁之城是什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.54,0:24:27.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这个铁块就是在北壁之上飞行的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.51,0:24:30.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是城池而是船
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.18,0:24:32.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做航空母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.59,0:24:34.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,航空母…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.05,0:24:38.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？这是船？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.28,0:24:40.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我有东西想给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.81,0:24:41.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,请到这边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.03,0:24:46.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大尉 你虽然是航空兵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.11,0:24:49.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但只要是海军的士官都应该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.63,0:24:54.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然几乎都被水浸湿了或被炸飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.42,0:24:57.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因为原本的数量比较多 所以有少许能用的装备还剩下来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.42,0:25:02.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们海军有在舰内准备能让船员在突发时
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.80,0:25:08.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,编组一支陆战队的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.06,0:25:11.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.66,0:25:15.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是有的嘛 毕竟是飞龙
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.50,0:25:18.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小狗狗 试试拿着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.55,0:25:20.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,请住手 天空神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.38,0:25:21.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.71,0:25:22.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.12,0:25:24.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这次又是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.91,0:25:25.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,枪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.84,0:25:26.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,步枪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.94,0:25:29.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,西庇阿先生
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.37,0:25:31.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你真的是西庇阿
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.25,0:25:36.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 这里是有来自遥远未来的武器的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.63,0:25:38.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,遥远未来？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.87,0:25:41.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因为和迦太基的战争是发生在公元前的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.16,0:25:45.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这是大约两千年以后的未来的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.86,0:25:47.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,两…两千
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.59,0:25:52.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,提督快看看这个 快看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.43,0:25:54.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「野狗黑吉」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.43,0:25:54.21,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,注：「野狗黑吉」，出自「のらくろ放浪记」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.35,0:25:55.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有只「野狗黑吉」在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.95,0:25:58.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人不是穿人偶服的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.49,0:26:01.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 「野狗黑吉」二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.80,0:26:03.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,提督
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.32,0:26:06.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,请把这两千年来的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.34,0:26:09.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大概也行 能不能告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.17,0:26:14.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是这两千年发展起来的军事方面的技术 武器
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.13,0:26:16.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,思考 思想
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.56,0:26:18.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,战术 革新
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.04,0:26:20.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,仅你所知也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.90,0:26:22.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.32,0:26:25.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是一介海军军人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.11,0:26:29.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只能告诉你一些零碎的 大体的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.74,0:26:30.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.12,0:26:32.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我会自己理解
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.98,0:26:34.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我很擅长学习
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.80,0:26:36.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我连汉尼拔也追得上了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.00,0:26:40.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这次就让我来试着追赶这两千年的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.60,0:28:14.16,Drifters Top,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HD9D9D9&\3c&H000000&\pos(774.667,351.667)}萨摩剧场
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.81,0:28:15.46,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HDBDBDB&}{\pos(640,566.333)}工作的处男
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.40,0:28:16.95,Drifters Top,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HBCBCBC&\3c&H000000&\pos(774.667,351.667)}玛蒙平原
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.73,0:28:27.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,Nowhere to Hide
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:05.87,difters-op,,0,0,0,,发动引擎 给我动力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:10.34,difters-op,,0,0,0,,踩下油门 奏响福音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:11.05,difters-op,,0,0,0,,歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:11.05,difters-op,,0,0,0,,{\an2}sing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:24.79,difters-op,,0,0,0,,疾驰 在这蜿蜒曲折中突进
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:27.73,difters-op,,0,0,0,,已欲罢不能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:31.23,difters-op,,0,0,0,,这是飓风般的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:34.40,difters-op,,0,0,0,,感受到了我的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.51,0:05:36.78,difters-op,,0,0,0,,感受到了这份爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:39.24,difters-op,,0,0,0,,正是狂奔的飓风
