Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.71,0:27:31.83,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}こんなにくべる炎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.71,0:27:31.83,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如此久久不息的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.00,0:27:34.34,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明けぬ夜は無いと
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.00,0:27:34.34,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不存在永不破晓的黑夜
